  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个事件生命周期的时序图，展示从用户创建到系统级更新的完整流程。第一阶段应该是用户手动创建v1版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created v1",
        "阶段1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那第二阶段是用户更新到v2吗？还有，Created v1这个状态在后续阶段会重复出现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Updated v2",
        "Created v1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第二阶段用户更新到v2。而且v1的创建记录要保留在第二阶段下面作为历史痕迹。第三阶段进入系统自动化流程，系统创建v3，同时要显示之前的v2更新和v1创建记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "阶段2",
        "阶段3",
        "System Created (v1) v3",
        "Updated v2",
        "Created v1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前三个阶段画出来。阶段3下面挂三个状态：System Created (v1) v3、Updated v2、Created v1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "阶段3",
        "System Created (v1) v3",
        "Updated v2",
        "Created v1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后需要第四阶段，系统更新到v4，同时保留系统创建v1的记录。注意这里v4的括号里是v2，表示基于v2的系统级更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "阶段4",
        "System Updated (v2) v4",
        "System Created (v1)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，第四阶段只有一个System Updated (v2) v4和一个System Created (v1)对吗？不需要再带Updated v2和Created v1了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "阶段4",
        "System Updated (v2) v4",
        "System Created (v1)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，第四阶段只保留系统层面的两个记录，用户操作的历史不再重复展示，这样层次更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "阶段4",
        "System Updated (v2) v4",
        "System Created (v1)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。标题定为\"Event Lifecycle\"，四个阶段依次展开，从用户创建v1开始，经过用户更新、系统创建，最终到系统更新v4，每个阶段的历史状态都按你的要求分层展示了。",
